[To] Jedonek Bolossj

[NPC Internal] Hello, is there any way I can help you?
[NPC Narrate] -The Ojaveda Guard flips his tail in boredom.-
[NPC Narrate] Jedonek Bolossj straightens up as you speak to him.
[NPC] Jedonek Bolossj: Hello citizen.
[NPC] Jedonek Bolossj: Remember to sheathe your weapon while in the Dsar.
[NPC] Jedonek Bolossj: May I help you find something or someone?
[NPC Internal] These doors are huge and there are so many of them. Who carved these gates? and when? And why?
[NPC Narrate] Jedonek Bolossj is surprised and glares at you.
[NPC] Jedonek Bolossj: Did Vetasor Knemal send you?
[NPC] Jedonek Bolossj: He's always trying to get one up on me because I have the better post.
[NPC Internal] [You shake your head.] No, I'm just wondering. Idle curiosity, I guess. Do you know about these carved gates, like who carved them?
[NPC Narrate] Jedonek Bolossj looks at the gates and shrugs.
[NPC] Jedonek Bolossj: I don't know.
[NPC] Jedonek Bolossj: Funny, I see them every day, and I've never thought about it.
[NPC] Jedonek Bolossj: They've been here forever as far as I know.
[NPC Narrate] -A twinkle comes into his eyes.-
[NPC] Jedonek Bolossj: You know, this is my chance to get one up on Vetasor!
[NPC] Jedonek Bolossj: That Enkidukai irks my tail, I tell you!
[NPC] Jedonek Bolossj: He thinks he knows everything, but I bet he doesn't know about these gates.
[NPC] Jedonek Bolossj: It would be worth it to me to find out more about them, so I can be the one who knows something for a change!
[NPC] Jedonek Bolossj: Would you be willing to find out everything you can about these gates?
[NPC] Jedonek Bolossj: I'll give you a reward for your efforts, especially if Vetasor doesn't know!
[NPC Internal] Yes, I like puzzles and I don't like know-it-alls either! I'm game. I'll do it!
[NPC Narrate] Jedonek Bolossj suggests.
[NPC] Jedonek Bolossj: You could ask the cook in the mess hall, she's old.
[NPC] Jedonek Bolossj: Maybe she knows.
[NPC] Jedonek Bolossj: Just come back and tell me when you find out?
[NPC] Jedonek Bolossj: It gets...
[NPC] Jedonek Bolossj: Boring.
[NPC] Jedonek Bolossj: Just standing here.

